              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EXTB",
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After irradiations waiting and",
                "measuring times were selected depending on the",
                "half-life of the isotope in interest so two-type",
                "irradiations were done for long and short",
                "half-lives radioisotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The natural Ag targets (107Ag - 58.83%, 109Ag - 48.17%)",
                "were 25 mg/cm thick corresponding to an average proton",
                "energy loss of 0.3 MeV and were irradiated in air.",
                "Below 18 MeV beam energies were degraded by Al foils.",
                "At 4 MeV the resulting energy spread of the proton beam",
                "due to the overall energy degrading was less than 1 MeV"
              ]
            }
          ],
